---
// src/components/About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About the Tournament</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                The Sam Lower Memorial Golf Tournament celebrates Sam's life and legacy, bringing together family, friends, and the Indianapolis community in his honor. 
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Honoring Sam's Memory</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Sam Lower was passionate about golf and brought joy to everyone around him. This tournament brings together family, friends, and the Indianapolis community to celebrate his life and the positive impact he made on others.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Supporting Research</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Proceeds from the tournament will benefit multiple myeloma research and support organizations, helping to advance treatment and find a cure for this disease.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Tournament Details Coming Soon</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                We're finalizing the date, venue, and format details. Sign up below to be the first to know when registration opens.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                <span class="flex items-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Date TBD
                </span>
                <span class="flex items-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Indianapolis Area
                </span>
                <span class="flex items-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                        </svg>
                    Entry Fee TBD
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>